  <div class="topic">
    <h3>Intro</h3>
    <p>By now you've at least spent a million hours in Codecademy coding up HTML. Now it's time we do this from scratch to build real pages. In this lessons we will learn:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>How to navigate through your computer from the command-line.</li>
      <li>How to create new files/folders from the command-line.</li>
      <li>The setup code (boilderplate) required for every website we build.</li>  
    </ul>

    <p>We'll do this by starting what will be your portfolio. At the end of the week you'll have live website deployed for the world to see!</p>
  </div>

